quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  43,74,"Toto abetsimbi baliba mushinyasio shia mumulilo kwa Jahannam tsinyanga tsioosi."
  43,75,"Shibalihulusibwa okhurulana nende eshinyasio esho tawe, ne omo baliwesiakhwo omwoyo (okhurulamwo) muno."
  43,76,"Ne shikhwabakholela amabii tawe, halali boo abeene nibo bali abamabii."
  43,77,"Ne balikhupa oluyoka nibalanga: “Ewe Malik! Boolela Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi akhufwisie.” Naye alibaboolela mbu: “Enywe toto omo butswa nimwamulamenya.”"
  43,78,"Toto khwabetsela nende obwatoto, halali abanji mwinywe mwali mwakhaya obwatoto."
  43,79,"Nohomba babusia amalako kabu. Ne toto nefwe babusinjia."
  43,80,"Nohomba baparanga mbu efwe shikhuwulilanga akobwifisi nende kokhumonyana kabu tawe? Eeh tawe. Abarumwa befu bali ninabo bahandikanga kabakholanga."
  43,81,"Boola mbu: “Nyasaye abetsanga nende Omwana, nesie wakhabeele weyimbeli okhumulaama.”"
  43,82,"Ni omutswenufu Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo, Nyasaye Omulesi weshisaala shioluyali ehale nende koosi kabamureetsangakhwo."
  43,83,"Ne baleshe bakoyaane nibabaya, okhula shinga balinyoolana nende inyanga yabalakwa."
  43,84,"Naye niye Nyasaye mwikulu khandi ni Nyasaye mushialo, naye niye Omuchesi, Omumanyi muno."
  43,85,"Ni woluyali ulia owuli nobwami bwomwikulu nende mushialo, nende bioosi bilimwo, ne niye uli nobumanyi bwebise bieyindukho, ne ewuwe ni wamulikalusibwa."
  43,86,"Ne abamulaamanga abalali Ye tawe babula obunyali bwokhusabila Omundu eshileshelo, halali ulia wobuloli bwatoto, nabo bamanya."
  43,87,"Ne nobareeba mbu ni wina wabaloonga bo? Toto bweene balaboola mbu: "Ni Nyasaye." Kho ni hena wabakalukhanibungwa?"
  43,88,"Ne okhuboola khukhwe (Omurumwa) mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, bano ni Abandu balasuubila tawe.”"
  43,89,"Kho baleshele ne baboolele amakhuwa komuleembe. Baliitsa okhumanya!"